<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Pendaftaran Berhasil - Dental Gama</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container text-center mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-success">Pendaftaran Berhasil!</h1>
    <p class="lead mt-3">Terima kasih, <strong><%= nama %></strong>, Anda telah berhasil mendaftar di Klinik Gigi Dental Gama.</p>
    
    <h4>Detail Pendaftaran</h4>
    <ul class="list-group mt-3">
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Nama:</strong> <%= nama %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>NIK:</strong> <%= nik %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>No. HP:</strong> <%= nohp %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Alamat:</strong> <%= alamat %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Jenis Kelamin:</strong> <%= jk === 'L' ? 'Laki-laki' : 'Perempuan' %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Tanggal Lahir:</strong> <%= moment(tgl_lahir).format('DD-MM-YYYY') %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Tanggal Periksa:</strong> <%= moment(tanggal).format('DD-MM-YYYY') %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Keluhan:</strong> <%= keluhan %></li>
      <li class="list-group-item"><strong>ID Pendaftaran:</strong> <code><%= id %></code></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-4">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>